cff-version: 1.2.0

message: >-
  Please cite the software using the repository metadata below.
  The associated master's thesis is listed under references.

title: "GHA-AIOps: Software for Anomaly Detection in GitHub Actions Pipelines"
type: software

authors:
  - family-names: "Ožvald"
    given-names: "Dominik"
    orcid: "<ORCID-URL>"
    affiliation: >-
      University of Zagreb Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Computing

version: "<VERSION>"
date-released: "<YYYY-MM-DD>"

repository-code: "https://github.com/DominikOzvald/msc-dominik-ozvald-2026"
url: "https://github.com/DominikOzvald/msc-dominik-ozvald-2026"
license: MIT

abstract: >-
  Software for training, evaluating, and integrating deep-learning models
  for anomaly detection in GitHub Actions pipeline logs. The repository
  accompanies Dominik Ožvald's 2026 master's thesis.

keywords:
  - AIOps
  - anomaly detection
  - GitHub Actions
  - CI/CD
  - log analysis
  - deep learning
  - transformer
  - autoencoder

